tyle="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Barry Tootell</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">: We ha</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">d</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> undoubtedly been busy, to say the least, considering the Verde opportunity, in and among managing the BAU business.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q558 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Jesse Norman:</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> So you were being massively stretched at that time?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Barry Tootell</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">: We were stretched, but that did not stop us doing the right thing by the business and at the same time considering the opportunity, and at the same time embracing the Unity programme.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q559 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size: